The Taste

She had almost forgotten
the taste 
of being loved in return
so rich
an intoxicating flavor
its juices
racing down her throat
searching within
not to sate her
but to fill her
and flow throughout
every part of her being
to sustain her
to fuel her
to sharpen and brighten
all of her senses
to make her come alive
Then she remembered 

Midnight Musings by 
Tammi Brown Keech
2023
